{"title":"Front Matter","markdown":{"headingText":"Front Matter","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n::: {.content-visible unless-format=\"pdf\" unless-format=\"epub\"}\n\n## How to Use\n\n**How to Access this Book in Other Formats**\n\n- **EPUB:** click <i class=\"bi bi-download\"></i> in the left-hand sidebar\n    - EPUB's benefits include accessibility, manipulability (via eReader options), dynamic media, interactivity, reflowable text, and offline reading\n- **PDF:** click <i class=\"bi bi-download\"></i> in the left-hand sidebar\n    - PDF's benefits include printability of physical copies\n- **Quarto Markdown (QMD):** click \"<i class=\"bi bi-github\"></i> View source\" in the right-hand sidebar\n    - QMD's benefits include reusability (revising, remixing, reformatting, repurposing, etc.) via a universal format\n- **TeX:** click \"<i class=\"bi bi-github\"></i> View source\" in the right-hand sidebar; then in the left-hand sidebar, select \"Afterthought.tex\"\n    - (La)TeX's benefits include advanced document formatting and typesetting \n\n:::\n\n**How to Report a Problem (Technological, Accessibility, Textual, Etc.) with this Book**\n\nClick \"Report an issue\" in the right-hand sidebar of the [HTML version](https://iulibscholcomm.github.io/afterthought/); then complete and submit the bug report.  \n\n::: {.content-visible unless-format=\"pdf\" unless-format=\"epub\"}\n\n**To Learn More**\n\nTo learn more about how to use the HTML book, see [Quarto's Guide](https://quarto.org/docs/guide/), or try its features.\n\n:::\n\n::: {.content-visible unless-format=\"pdf\"}\n\n## Copyright and License\n\n&copy; 2025 Heather Akou\\\n\n<p xmlns:cc=\"http://creativecommons.org/ns#\" xmlns:dct=\"http://purl.org/dc/terms/\"><span property=\"dct:title\">Afterthought: A Family Story</span> by <a rel=\"cc:attributionURL dct:creator\" property=\"cc:attributionName\" href=\"https://www.heatherakou.net/\">Heather Akou</a> is licensed under <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/l